---
// Componente Hero institucional para Colegio Alpha
---
<section id="inicio" class="pt-28 pb-16   bg-gradient-to-br from-[#05ff6d1f] via-[#ffffff2c] to-[#2a64f836] relative overflow-hidden ">
  <div class="absolute inset-0  w-full  bg-center bg-cover opacity-60 z-10" style="background-image: url('506744486_122100663782930751_2872311345080472222_n.jpg');"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white  "></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 px-4">
    <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center md:justify-start animate-fade-in">
      <img src="/logo.webp" alt="Logo Colegio Alpha" class="h-56 w-56 md:h-72 md:w-72 drop-shadow-2xl z-20" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-right z-20 bg-white/50 p-4 rounded-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-logo-azul)] mb-4 leading-tight animate-fade-in-up">Colegio Alpha</h1>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-[var(--color-logo-verde)] font-bold mb-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">de Pachuca</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-00 drop-shadow-2xl font-bold mb-8 animate-fade-in-up delay-300">En Colegio Alpha de Pachuca nos comprometemos con la formación integral de tus hijos, desarrollando sus habilidades en entornos científicos y tecnológicos con valores.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-400">
        <a href="#inscripcion" class="inline-block bg-[var(--color-logo-azul)] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-[var(--color-logo-verde)] hover:text-white transition">¡Inscríbete hoy!</a>
        <a href="#filosofia" class="inline-block bg-white text-[var(--color-logo-azul)] px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg shadow-lg border-2 border-[var(--color-logo-azul)] hover:bg-[var(--color-logo-azul)] hover:text-white transition">Conoce más</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section> 